# demos/file-io.tape — File read, write, and str_replace
Output demos/file-io.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "hello"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "!!cat src/main.cpp"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "what does this code do?"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "fix the typo on line 12"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "y"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "exit"
Enter
